{"tid":861431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慈正邨八旬婦飲蚊怕水自殺昏迷送院不治","createTime":"2018-10-14T06:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T06:38:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30d4ea435bd54b155a87c0b75269797f9f222931","tid":861431,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"黃大仙慈正邨一名81歲老婦，早上懷疑喝下蚊怕水自殺，昏迷送院搶救後死亡，死因有待驗屍後確定。。<br />\n<br />\n現場為慈正邨正德樓一單位。警方早上9時48分接獲事主81歲的丈夫報案，指發現同齡的妻子喝下蚊怕水，懷疑她自殺。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，女事主昏迷送廣華醫院後被證實死亡。警方在現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1340409/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1340409%2F&d=m6G9QNRFau2K256fxrbYNC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=535dcbd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1340409%2F&h=7b430b87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1340409/</a>"},{"pid":"9f5064923ba9c9ce401f404127cca5a7d49c43ed","tid":861431,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"咁難飲 點飲呀"},{"pid":"5b3822a51ec567374a4232fdd269fc45aa777c25","tid":861431,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:37:39.000Z","msg":"都8十幾咁睇唔開"},{"pid":"74ec1b666feee7cdf393b9eb1c5ae0cd0ba960fd","tid":861431,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:37:40.000Z","msg":"以為飲左先驅到蚊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6077d985fc33e13095dcf8bfb0acf036af4641","tid":861431,"uid":3976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"佢諗住防登隔熱咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"}]}